{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7fab4494-263f-4772-a230-8e14cf1240ba","content":"Now I have a clear picture. Here are the key xUnit v3 migration changes needed:\n\n1. **`.csproj`**: Replace v2 packages with `xunit.v3`, add `Exe` output type, remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` and `xunit.runner.visualstudio`\n2. **`global.json`**: Switch runner from `VSTest` to `Microsoft.Testing.Platform`\n3. **Test code**: No changes needed — `[Fact]`, `[Theory]`, and `Assert` APIs are compatible","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01C8CD63NXv5oQeJwerVnjp9","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-ca6326580aaa4deaa9c858e68cd4f940/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>\n    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>\n    <IsPackable>false</IsPackable>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk\" Version=\"18.3.0\" />\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit\" Version=\"2.9.3\" />\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.runner.visualstudio\" Version=\"2.8.2\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>","new_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>\n    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>\n    <IsPackable>false</IsPackable>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3\" Version=\"1.1.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-ca6326580aaa4deaa9c858e68cd4f940/TestProject.csproj."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_015x1WuDE2FzSocfJTqSqEoX","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-ca6326580aaa4deaa9c858e68cd4f940/global.json","old_str":"{\n  \"test\": {\n    \"runner\": \"VSTest\"\n  }\n}","new_str":"{\n  \"test\": {\n    \"runner\": \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\"\n  }\n}"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-ca6326580aaa4deaa9c858e68cd4f940/global.json."}],"interactionId":"b89732cb-9848-4ff8-993f-8e0d6eaead01","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I understand the current state. Let me migrate from xUnit.net v2 to v3. Here are the key changes needed:\n\n1. **Project file (TestProject.csproj)**:\n   - Change `OutputType` to `Exe` (xUnit v3 tests are executables, not libraries)\n   - Replace `xunit` package with `xunit.v3`\n   - Remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` (not needed for v3)\n   - Remove `xunit.runner.visualstudio` (not needed for v3)\n   - Add `xunit.runner.visualstudio` v3 or use the new runner approach\n   - Keep `IsPackable` set to false\n\n2. **Test file (CalculatorTests.cs)**:\n   - The namespace remains `Xunit` in v3, so that part doesn't change\n   - `[Fact]` and `[Theory]` attributes work the same way\n   - `Assert.Equal` and other assertions remain unchanged\n\n3. **global.json**:\n   - For xUnit v3, the test runner configuration needs to switch from `VSTest` to `\"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\"` to work properly with `dotnet test`\n\nLooking at the key migration steps for xUnit v3: swap out the v2 `xunit` package for `xunit.v3`, remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` and `xunit.runner.visualstudio` since the runner is now built-in.\n\nI also need to add `<OutputType>Exe</OutputType>` to the project file since v3 treats test projects as executables, update the runner configuration in global.json, and the test code itself stays in the `Xunit` namespace. Let me start making these changes.","outputTokens":1281,"requestId":"B840:71272:2E92918:31713DB:6A0493B2"},"id":"96e531cc-0ef5-4f3d-8f79-e6763bb95a85","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:07:49.527Z","parentId":"173b62e7-b3f7-41fa-aa4d-2e119c39347e"}
